    "causal_summary": "Retrieval-rescue (default ON) overwrites the final score of every candidate with `0.03base + 0.78lexicalOverlap` (`retrieval-rescue.ts:210`, applied at `stage2-fusion.ts:1425`), so learned trigger boosts (+0.7), negative demotions (x0.3), graph, recency, and co-activation signals are compressed to at most 3.7% of ranking mass (a +0.7 learned boost lands as <=0.021); only the validation multiplier at `stage2-fusion.ts:1470` runs after rescue and survives (deep-dive report Chain D; ledger Agent G P1)",
